Class PokemonType

java.lang.Object
  org.jpokemon.pmapi.type.PokemonType
Direct Known Subclasses:
BugType, DarkType, DragonType, ElectricType, FightingType, FireType, FlyingType, GhostType, GrassType, GroundType, IceType, NormalType, PoisonType, PsychicType, RockType, SteelType, TypelessType, WaterType
public abstract class PokemonType
extends Object

Defines an abstract Pokémon type (such as Grass or Dark) that must be extended to create a class for each type. The classic 17 types are instantiated by the ClassicTypes class.
